{
  "stem": "490.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I knew it was impossible to-- here I am, in the center in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it's amazing how strong you are when you are young.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were able to get organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Of course, life had no meaning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Of course, at the time, they said, you go-- can go in any place and-- and take anything you want.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went into some buildings, some houses, which there were Nazis-- officers, or generals, or whatever-- all kinds of high-class military men.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The only thing we could think is to destroy some mirrors, to break some furniture, to get a little of our [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] hatred, express your feelings.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember I came into a house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was so much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I think today, probably the-- some beautiful paintings and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The only thing I walked out with was a little cocoa, which in the kitchen-- that's what I took.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I walked out with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I did not think of any future.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Or let me see, maybe this painting is a-- it is a famous van Gogh or a Picasso.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, anything you [INAUDIBLE], you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Nobody, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Nothing mattered to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it took-- it took us-- took me a long time to-- to realize that money means anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Of course, in the beginning, you didn't have to have any money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, you-- you went into the store.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
